replies.body:
I've said it before and I'll say it again;

Riot needs to bring back Tribunal and have video playback for reports of griefing. Automated system can stay for reports of hate speech but bring back Tribunal.

I don't care if that guy who inted in my game is banned 8 months later, as long as I know he's banned. Imagine saying the justice system is flawed because people are arrested months after their crime.
